	('JordanOpen2019', 'Jordan Open 2019', 'Amman', 'Jordan', '**عربي:**\r\nيرجى الضغط على **معلومات اخرى** للحصول على تفاصيل اخرى\r\n\r\n**English:**\r\nPlease refer to the **More Info.** tab for more details.', 2019, 7, 27, 2019, 7, 27, 0, '222 333 444 pyram', '[{Aysha Jamsheer}{mailto:ajamsheer@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Aysha Jamsheer}{mailto:ajamsheer@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Baha Alshwaiki}{mailto:balshwaiki@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Clément Cherblanc}{mailto:ccherblanc@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Fuad Ali}{mailto:fuadrubiks@gmail.com}]', 'Omareyah Schools. المدارس العمرية - ثانوية البنين', 'Omareyah School, Ayaman Ramdan St 3, Amman, Jordan', 'School Theatre. مسرح المدرسة', NULL, 'Jordan Open 2019', 31982482, 35889238),
	('KosovoOpen2023', 'Kosovo Open 2023', 'Prishtina', 'Kosovo', 'For more information check out the tabs!', 2023, 6, 25, 2023, 6, 25, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 pyram skewb', '[{Aleksandar Arsovski}{mailto:aarsovski@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Samuel Mema}{mailto:samuelmema33@gmail.com}]', '[{Aleksandar Arsovski}{mailto:aarsovski@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Lir Ukaj}{mailto:hikmetukaj@gmail.com}]', '[International School of Prishtina](https://ispkosova.com/)', 'Preoc, Marigona Residence, International School of Prishtina / Gracanica 10000', 'Sports hall', NULL, 'Kosovo Open 2023', 42585061, 21106898),
	('LaMassana2021', 'La Massana 2021', 'La Massana', 'Andorra', 'Revisa l\'[horari](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/LaMassana2021#competition-schedule). Allà hi trobaràs tota la planificació de la competició. Es prega molta puntualitat. Et recomanem arribar mitja hora abans de cada prova a la qual competeixis.\r\n\r\nLlegeix detingudament la pestanya sobre la [COVID-19](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/LaMassana2021#16408-covid-19) amb els principals canvis de la competició a causa de la situació sanitària.\r\n\r\n--------\r\n\r\nRevisa el [horario](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/LaMassana2021#competition-schedule). Allí encontraràs toda la planificación de la competición. Se ruega mucha puntualidad. Te recomendamos llegar media hora antes de cada prueba en la que compitas.\r\n\r\nLee detenidamente la pestaña sobre el [COVID-19](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/LaMassana2021#16408-covid-19) con los principales cambios de la competición debido a la situación sanitaria.\r\n\r\n--------\r\n\r\nCheck the [schedule](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/LaMassana2021#competition-schedule). There you can see all the planning of the competition. Please be very punctual. We recommend you to arrive half hour in advance for each event you compete in.\r\n\r\nRead carefully the tab about [COVID-19](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/LaMassana2021#16408-covid-19) with the main changes in the competition due to the health situation.', 2021, 10, 30, 2021, 10, 31, 0, '222 333 333fm 333oh 444 555 clock pyram skewb sq1', '[{Javier Tirado Ortiz}{mailto:jortiz@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Club de Rubik de Catalunya}{mailto:wca@rubik.cat}] [{Marcos Ameijeiras Moreno}{mailto:marcos@rubik.cat}] [{Pablo Nicolás Oshiro Mondoñedo}{mailto:pabloosmo@hotmail.com}] [{Pau Vela García}{mailto:pau.vela.garcia@gmail.com}]', '[La Closeta](https://www.lamassana.ad/serveis-equipaments/teatre-fontetes-sales-comunals)', 'Av. de Sant Antoni, 29, AD400 La Massana, Andorra', '', 'https://www.rubik.cat/campionats/la-massana-2021', 'La Massana 2021', 42544860, 1515505),
	('LightsOfReykjavik2019', 'Lights of Reykjavik 2019', 'Hafnarfjörður', 'Iceland', '**Walk in registrations will be allowed until we reach the limit of registration**\r\n\r\nSpace in the venue is limited, please let us know how many people will come with you.\r\nYou will have to pay the registration fees at the venue the day of the competition to participate: kr1500 (~11€)\r\n________\r\n\r\nPláss á staðnum er takmarkað svo endilega látið okkur vita hversu marga gesti þið munuð hafa með ykkur.\r\nMótsgjald er 1500 krónur fyrir keppendur og verður það greitt á mótsdag.\r\n________\r\n.', 2019, 1, 4, 2019, 1, 5, 0, '222 333 333bf 333ft 333oh 444 555 666 777 clock minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Hari Anirudh}{mailto:harisv.1994@gmail.com}]', '[{Clément Cherblanc}{mailto:ccherblanc@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Danival Heide Sævarsson}{mailto:dsaevarsson@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Pétur Óskarsson}{mailto:petur@viator.is}] [{Rúnar Gauti Gunnarsson}{mailto:runarg2002@gmail.com}]', 'Flensborgarskólinn', 'Hringbraut 10, 220, Hafnarfjordur, Iceland', 'Follow the signs/ fylgið merkingunum', NULL, 'Lights of Reykjavik 2019', 64065124, -21951281),
	('LuandaOpen2023', 'Luanda Open 2023', 'Luanda', 'Angola', '🇦🇴 Bem-vindos à 1ª competição oficial da WCA em Angola!\r\n\r\nSua inscrição só será aprovada no site da WCA após a confirmação do pagamento, que deverá ser efetuado de forma antecipada - mais informações na aba [Inscrever](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/BrasiliaBigsBlind2023/register). Se tiver dificuldades em se inscrever, veja como fazer [neste vídeo](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-cJNjPk_J4M).\r\n\r\nFavor leia o [Regulamento da WCA](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/translations/portuguese-brazilian) antes da competição.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n🇺🇸 Welcome to the 1st WCA official competition in Angola!\r\n\r\nYour registration will only be approved in the WCA website after payment confirmation, which must be made in advance - more information in the [Register](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/BrasiliaBigsBlind2023/register) tab. If you have any problem with how to register, take a look at [this video](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-cJNjPk_J4M).\r\n\r\nPlease read the [WCA Regulations](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations) before the competition.', 2023, 5, 7, 2023, 5, 7, 0, '222 333 333oh', '[{Cláudio Vidal da Silva Morais}{mailto:vidalmorais84@gmail.com}] [{Marlon de V. Marques}{mailto:mmarques@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Cláudio Vidal da Silva Morais}{mailto:vidalmorais84@gmail.com}] [{Kahilo Pedro Massango}{mailto:kahilo42@gmail.com}] [{Manuel Ngola Cusseiala}{mailto:ngolakjr@gmail.com}] [{Marlon de V. Marques}{mailto:mmarques@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Roger Nataniel Issassa dos Santos}{mailto:rogerdossantos25@hotmail.com}] [{Vivaldo Cristóvão Roque}{mailto:2001vivaldo@gmail.com}]', 'Mediateca Zé Du - Cazenga', '574M+9CQ, Rua dos Comandos, Cazenga', 'Auditório', NULL, 'Luanda Open 2023', -8844037, 13283609),
	('LuxembourgPiDay2020', 'Luxembourg Pi Day 2020', 'Esch-sur-Alzette', 'Luxembourg', '# The competition is cancelled due to the COVID-19 outbreak.\r\n**English**\r\nWelcome to the second official competition in Luxembourg! If this is your first competition you can find some useful information on the \"Newcomer Information\" tab.\r\nThere is no registration fee for this competition, but if you want you can make a donation. The money collected this way will be used to help organize future competitions in Luxembourg. Please note that only online registration is is free. If you register on the spot the fee is 1€.\r\n\r\n**Deutsch**\r\nWillkommen zum zweiten offiziellen Wettbewerb in Luxemburg! Wenn dies dein erster Wettbewerb ist, findest du im Tab \"Newcomer Information\" nützliche Informationen.\r\nEs gibt keine Anmeldegebühr für diesen Wettbewerb, aber wenn du möchtest, kannst du eine Spende machen. Das auf diese Weise gesammelte Geld wird für die Organisation zukünftiger Wettbewerbe in Luxemburg verwendet. Bitte beachte dass nur die Online Registration kostenlos ist. Wenn du dich vor Ort registrierst bezahlst du 1€.\r\n\r\n**Français**\r\nBienvenue à la deuxième compétition du Luxembourg! Si c\'est votre première compétition, il y a des informations très utiles dans l\'onglet \"Newcomer Information\".\r\nIl n\'y a pas de frais d\'inscription pour cette competition, mais tu peux malgré tout faire un don. L\'argent collecté servira à organiser des futur competitions. Veuillez noter que seule l‘inscription en ligne est gratuite.  L\'inscription sur place sera à 1€.\r\n\r\n**Lëtzebuergesch**\r\nWëllkomm zu der zweeter offizieller Compétitioun zu Lëtzebuerg! Wann dëst deng éischt Compétitioun ass, da fënns du am Tab \"Newcomer Informations\" nëtzlech Informatiounen.\r\nEt kascht näischt matzemaachen, mee wanns du wëlls, kanns du gären eng Spend maachen. Dës Suen ginn agesat fir weider Compétitionen zu Lëtzebuerg ze organiséieren! Nëmmen wanns du dech online registréiers ass ett gratis. Wanns du dech um Event selwer umells, kascht ett dëch 1€.', 2020, 3, 14, 2020, 3, 14, 1, '222 333 333bf 444 minx pyram skewb', '[{Tobias Peter}{mailto:tobias.peter@bluewin.ch}]', '[{Andrea Thull}{mailto:andreathull@gmail.com}] [{Carlo Glod}{mailto:carlo.glod@gmail.com}] [{Joe Theis}{mailto:joe@theis.lu}] [{Philippe Schwartz}{mailto:schwartz.philippe@hotmail.com}] [{Sebastiano Tronto}{mailto:stronto@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[Maison du Savoir, Belval campus](https://wwwen.uni.lu/contact/campus_de_belval)', '2 Avenue de l\'Universite, 4365 Esch-sur-Alzette, Luxembourg', 'Main university building, 4th floor', NULL, 'Luxembourg Pi Day 2020', 49504552, 5948429),
	('MacauOpen2009', 'Macau Rubik\'s Open 2009', 'Macau', 'Macau', '', 2009, 8, 15, 2009, 8, 15, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 magic mmagic', '[{Chan Tak Chuen (陳德泉)}{mailto:tchan@worldcubeassociation.org}]', NULL, '[Macau Fisherman´s Wharf](http://www.fishermanswharf.com.mo)', 'Avenida da Amizade e Avenida Dr.Sun Yat-Sen', '', 'http://hkcubeunion.net/mo09', 'Macau Rubik\'s Open 2009', 22195203, 113554830),
	('MacedoniaWinter2019', 'Macedonia Winter 2019', 'Skopje', 'North Macedonia', 'For more information check out the tabs!', 2019, 2, 2, 2019, 2, 3, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 minx pyram skewb', '[{Tobias Peter}{mailto:tobias.peter@bluewin.ch}]', '[{Aleksandar Arsovski}{mailto:aarsovski@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Reto Bubendorf}{mailto:retobubendorf@gmail.com}]', 'Hotel Aleksandar Palace, Skopje', 'Prohor Pcinjski, Skopje 1000', 'Congress hall (there will be signs on the venue)', NULL, 'Macedonia Winter 2019', 42010787, 21405594),
	('MadagascarCubingOpen2019', 'Madagascar Cubing Open 2019', 'Antananarivo', 'Madagascar', 'Madagascar will host for the first time a WCA competition !\r\n\r\nOnly Malagasy competitors are eligible for prizes and podiums.\r\n_____\r\nMadagascar accueillera pour la première fois une compétition de la WCA !\r\n\r\nSeulement les compétiteurs Malgaches sont eligibles pour les prix et podiums.', 2019, 6, 1, 2019, 6, 1, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 555', '[{Akash Rupela}{mailto:arupela@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Andy Rasoanarivo}{mailto:okalouservices@gmail.com}] [{Clément Cherblanc}{mailto:ccherblanc@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Malagasy Association of Cubers}{mailto:mg.associationmac@gmail.com}]', 'Skate Park ', 'Skate Park Antanimena', 'Inside the Skate Park', NULL, 'Madagascar Cubing Open 2019', -18897946, 47523840),
	('MaltaOpen2019', 'Malta Open 2019', 'Msida', 'Malta', 'This is the first WCA competition in Malta. It is an open competition for all people from all ages and all countries.\r\nWe hope many people from Malta and other countries will participate.\r\n\r\nThe competition also counts as the national championship for Malta.\r\nSo the best competitors from Malta will be the national champions 2019 of Malta.\r\n\r\nDoors are open from 8:30am.', 2019, 11, 30, 2019, 11, 30, 0, '222 333 333bf 444 555 pyram skewb', '[{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{James Golding}{mailto:jamesgolding1337@gmail.com}] [{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[The University of Malta](https://www.um.edu.mt/)', 'Mathematics and Physics Building, University of Malta, Msida MSD 2080, Malta.', 'Room MP401', NULL, 'Malta Open 2019', 35903086, 14484349),
	('MauritiusOpen2020', 'Mauritius Open 2020', 'Moka', 'Mauritius', 'The competition will happen in the Gymnasium, kindly follow the posters to reach the venue.', 2020, 2, 23, 2020, 2, 23, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 pyram', '[{Milind Bhoyroo}{mailto:mbhoyroo@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Milind Bhoyroo}{mailto:mbhoyroo@worldcubeassociation.org}]', 'Lycée des Mascareignes', 'Lycée des Mascareignes, Helvetia, Saint Pierre', 'The competition will happen in the Gymnasium, kindly follow the posters to reach the venue.', NULL, 'Mauritius Open 2020', -20227087, 57524617),
	('MoldovaOpen2020', 'Moldova Open 2020', 'Chişinău', 'Moldova', 'This is the first WCA competition in Moldova since 2017. It is an open competition for all people of all ages and from all countries.\r\nWe hope many people from Moldova and other countries will participate.\r\n\r\nThe competition also counts as the national championship for Moldova.\r\nSo the best competitors from Moldova will be the national champions 2019 of Moldova.', 2020, 1, 11, 2020, 1, 11, 0, '222 333 333bf 444 555 pyram skewb', '[{Mihai Căpăţinescu}{mailto:mcapatinescu@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Costea Livadari}{mailto:livadari.costea@gmail.com}] [{Mihai Căpăţinescu}{mailto:mcapatinescu@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[Moldova State University](http://usm.md/?lang=en)', '60 Alexei Mateevici Str., Chişinău, MD-2009', 'Faculty of Mathematics and Computer Science, 4th Building, room Sala de Lectura, second floor.', NULL, 'Moldova Open 2020', 47018522, 28823824),
	('MontenegroOpen2019', 'Montenegro Open 2019', 'Podgorica', 'Montenegro', 'For more information check out the tabs!\r\nZa više informacija pogledajte tabove!', 2019, 2, 9, 2019, 2, 10, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Tobias Peter}{mailto:tobias.peter@bluewin.ch}]', '[{David Pantović}{mailto:davidpantovic24@gmail.com}] [{Reto Bubendorf}{mailto:retobubendorf@gmail.com}]', 'University of Montenegro', 'Bulevar Džordža Vašingtona, Podgorica', 'on the second floor, follow the signs', NULL, 'Montenegro Open 2019', 42443069, 19240667),
	('MoroccoSummer2019', 'Morocco Summer 2019', 'Rabat', 'Morocco', 'L\'inscription est ouverte à tout le monde jusqu\'à l\'atteinte de 50 compétiteurs inscrits.\r\nThe competition is open to everyone until the 50 competitor limit is reached.\r\nTime: 8am until 7pm.', 2019, 7, 7, 2019, 7, 7, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 minx', '[{Soufiane Lakhlifi}{mailto:slakhlifi@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Mohamed Elkhatri}{mailto:mohamed.elkhatri2002@gmail.com}] [{Omar Ouadouha}{mailto:omar.ouadouha1@gmail.com}]', 'École Nationale Supérieure des Mines de Rabat', 'Ecole Nationale supérieure des Mines de Rabat, Rabat', 'Salle des invités', NULL, 'Morocco Summer 2019', 34000312, -6854812),
	('NigeriaOpen2019', 'Nigeria Open 2019', 'Lagos', 'Nigeria', 'You\'re asked to have read the [WCA regulations](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/), the tutorial at the competition is here to remind them to you!\r\nIt is very important to attend to at least one of the tutorials so that you can understand how the competition goes and to avoid incidents!\r\n\r\nThe competition is open to all competitors, of all ages and all nationalities!', 2019, 5, 25, 2019, 5, 26, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 444bf 555 minx pyram skewb', '[{Soufiane Lakhlifi}{mailto:slakhlifi@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Arinze Owoh}{mailto:arinzeowoh@gmail.com}] [{Clément Cherblanc}{mailto:ccherblanc@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Kemi Awe}{mailto:kawe@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[Lycée Français Louis Pasteur](https://www.lflp-lagos.com)', '16 Younis Bashorun Street, Victoria Island, Lagos, Nigeria', 'Room: Salle des Droits de l\'Homme', NULL, 'Nigeria Open 2019', 6426613, 3436617),
	('OmanOpen2023', 'Oman Open 2023', 'Muscat', 'Oman', 'This is the first WCA competition in Oman.\r\nThe competition is the national championship of Oman for the year 2023. \r\nThe competition is open to all persons from all countries.\r\n\r\nThere will be prizes and honours:\r\n- top 3 competitors with the nationality of Oman\r\n- competitors without the nationality of Oman, who finish in top 3 of an event\r\n\r\n', 2023, 3, 11, 2023, 3, 11, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 555', '[{Aysha Jamsheer}{mailto:ajamsheer@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Baha Alshwaiki}{mailto:balshwaiki@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Baha Alshwaiki}{mailto:balshwaiki@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Farah Omar Alomar}{mailto:faroo7a_alomar@hotmail.com}] [{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[HORMUZ Grand Muscat hotel](https://www.radissonhotels.com/en-us/hotels/radisson-collection-muscat)', 'Al Matar St Muscat 111, 128, Oman', 'room Oryx 1', NULL, 'Oman Open 2023', 23576812, 58292062),
	('PakistanWinter2019', 'Pakistan Winter 2019', 'Islamabad', 'Pakistan', 'See tabs for more information about the competition.', 2019, 12, 21, 2019, 12, 21, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 555', '[{Abdullah Gulab}{mailto:agulab@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Abdullah Gulab}{mailto:agulab@worldcubeassociation.org}]', 'Air University', 'Service Rd E-9 / E-8, E-9, Islamabad', 'Main Auditorium', 'http://cubingpakistan.com/', 'Pakistan Winter 2019', 33713800, 73024700),
	('PalestineOpen2019', 'Palestine Open 2019', 'Al-Beira', 'Palestine', '', 2019, 7, 6, 2019, 7, 7, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 555 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Ilya Tsiareshka}{mailto:itsiareshka@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Ahmad Abu Hussein}{mailto:amah22222@yahoo.com}]', 'Baladeya Al Bireh', 'Baladeya Al Bireh, Al-Bireh,00970 Be\'Erot, West Bank', 'On the first floor far in the back', NULL, 'Palestine Open 2019', 31904212, 35212635),
	('PchelkaOpen2018', 'Pchelka Open 2018', 'Chopon-Ata, Issyk Kul', 'Kyrgyzstan', 'There is a competitor limit of 150 competitors. If you register and later decide to not attend the competition, please inform the organizers so another competitor can get a seat.\r\nЛимит участников 150 человек.Если вы зарегистрируетесь, а затем решите не участвовать в конкурсе, сообщите об этом организаторам.', 2018, 8, 22, 2018, 8, 23, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Akash Rupela}{mailto:arupela@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Akash Rupela}{mailto:arupela@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Clément Cherblanc}{mailto:ccherblanc@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Nadira Haroon}{mailto:nad_ira25@yahoo.com}] [{Nazira Shayimkulova}{mailto:pchelka.kg@gmail.com}]', 'Children\'s Camp Barchyn', 'Children\'s Camp Barchyn, Chon-Sary-Oy, Chopon-Ata, Issyk Kul, Kyrgyzstan', '', NULL, 'Pchelka Open 2018', 42609102, 76915328),
	('PragueOpen2023', 'Prague Open 2023', 'Prague', 'Czech Republic', '![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaHM1IiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--fc33ae9e439080ea857be81b152f0c14a55fe718/prague.png)\r\nPlease read carefully all the tabs! \r\n\r\nProsíme, přečtěte si pečlivě všechny záložky!', 2023, 6, 17, 2023, 6, 18, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Emma Beranová}{mailto:eberanova@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Jan Fonš}{mailto:honzafons@seznam.cz}]', '[{Arsenij Kuprin}{mailto:kuprin.ars@gmail.com}] [{Emma Beranová}{mailto:eberanova@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Tomáš Nguyen}{mailto:tomas.nguyen159@gmail.com}]', 'Základní škola a Mateřská škola Červený Vrch', 'Alžírská 26/680,  Praha 6 - Vokovice', 'Jídelna', NULL, 'Prague Open 2023', 50095384, 14353753),
	('Q8speedcubinginKSE2023', 'Q8speedcubing in K.S.E 2023', 'Bneid Al-Gar', 'Kuwait', 'أهلا بكم في مسابقة \r\nQ8speedcubing 2023.\r\nالعنوان :- الكويت - بنيد القار - شارع السور - جمعية المهندسين الكويتية - قاعة السرداب كما هو موضح في رابط خرائط جوجل \r\n\r\nWelcome to Q8speedcubing in K.S.E 2023 \r\nKuwait - Bnied Al-Gar - Soor St. - Kuwait Soceity of Engineers as shown in the Google maps link .\r\nThe competition is in hall in the basment .\r\n![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbHd3IiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--c8d2ceffa16f32641b740813db8e197348f3de2c/Q8.png)![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbDB3IiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--a1b63aa936b62d3e021c7dae0dfee8c7126069c8/K.S.E.jpg)\r\n\r\n', 2023, 3, 10, 2023, 3, 11, 0, '222 333 333bf 333fm 333mbf 333oh 444 555 clock minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Zakarya Otair}{mailto:zotair@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Mohammad Almoumen}{mailto:almoumn95@gmail.com}] [{Saoud Abdulaziz Almutawa}{mailto:almutawa002@gmail.com}]', 'Kuwait Society of Engineers  ', 'Soor St  Kuwait City, Kuwait', 'Theater in the basement of the building .', NULL, 'Q8speedcubing in K.S.E 2023', 29381720, 48002043),
	('RamliMallOpen2019', 'Ramli Mall Open 2019', 'Aali', 'Bahrain', '**عربي:**\r\nيرجى الضغط على**معلومات اخرى** للحصول على تفاصيل اخرى\r\n\r\n**English:**\r\nPlease refer to the **More Info.** tab for more details.', 2019, 11, 23, 2019, 11, 23, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 pyram skewb sq1', '[{Aysha Jamsheer}{mailto:ajamsheer@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Aysha Jamsheer}{mailto:ajamsheer@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Ebrahim Jamsheer}{mailto:jamsheerebrahim@hotmail.com}] [{Matteo Dummar}{mailto:mdummar@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Pulkit Mehra}{mailto:pulkitmehra18@gmail.com}]', 'Ramli Mall', 'Rd. No. 3025 Aali', 'Ramli Mall (Main Stage, Basement)', NULL, 'Ramli Mall Open 2019', 26163070, 50523056),
	('RodoOpen2020', 'Rodo Open 2020', 'Peso da Régua', 'Portugal', '# This competition is cancelled due to the COVID-19 outbreak. \r\n\r\n# Esta competição foi cancelada devido ao surto de COVID-19.\r\n', 2020, 3, 21, 2020, 3, 21, 1, '222 333 333bf 444 pyram', '[{António Gomes}{mailto:cubizh@gmail.com}]', '[{Didier Batista Ferreira}{mailto:didierbatista@hotmail.com}]', '[Escola Profissional de Desenvolvimento Rural do Rodo](https://www.epregua.pt)', 'Quinta do Rodo, Rua de Lousada – Godim, Peso da Régua, 5050-092 Peso da Régua', 'Cantina', NULL, 'Rodo Open 2020', 41177216, -7796323),
	('SarajevoOpen2019', 'Sarajevo Open 2019', 'Sarajevo', 'Bosnia and Herzegovina', 'Sarajevo Open 2019 is a speedcubing competition. Anyone can participate, who is familiar with the WCA Regulation, accepts it and meet the competition’s criterias.\r\n\r\n\r\nSarajevo Open 2019 je speedcubing takmičenje. Svako ko poznaje WCA pravila i ispunjava WCA zahtjeve može da učestvuje na takmičenju.\r\n', 2019, 10, 19, 2019, 10, 20, 0, '222 333 333bf 333fm 333oh 444 555 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Jernej Omulec}{mailto:jomulec@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Janko Gašić}{mailto:jankogasic@yahoo.com}] [{Jernej Omulec}{mailto:jomulec@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Marko Vukadinović}{mailto:markovukadinovic94@gmail.com}] [{Nebojša Đurić}{mailto:nebojsadjuric89@gmail.com}]', 'Faculty of Science / Prirodno-matematički fakultet', 'Zmaja od Bosne 33-35', 'Follow the signs ', NULL, 'Sarajevo Open 2019', 43854258, 18394610),
	('SaramadaCubingBangladesh2023', 'Saramada Cubing Bangladesh 2023', 'Dhaka', 'Bangladesh', '\r\n\r\n1. Competitors and guests MUST NOT attend this competition if they have any COVID-19 symptoms or have been in contact with someone who is COVID-19 positive.\r\n2. Please be aware that there are qualification criteria in place for participating in this competition. \r\n3. All the necessary information is given the Tabs, please have a look.\r\n4. Please follow the [Saramada Cubing Bangladesh 2023 ](http://facebook.com/SCBd23), all the updates will be posted there. \r\n\r\n', 2023, 6, 16, 2023, 6, 16, 0, '333 333fm 333oh', '[{Arnab Banik}{mailto:abanik@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Arnab Banik}{mailto:abanik@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Farhanul Haque Khan}{mailto:illusionkillerfahim@gmail.com}]', '[CubeNation HQ] (https://www.facebook.com/cubenationbd/)', 'CubeNation, House #91-93, Road #W2 ,Block-C, Eastern Housing, Pallabi, Dhaka 1216', '1st Floor, 1A', NULL, 'Saramada Cubing Bangladesh 2023', 23822167, 90352555),
	('SemeyOpen2018', 'Semey Open 2018', 'Semey', 'Kazakhstan', 'Dear competitors and guests!\r\n\r\n1. The official opening ceremony will be held on June 7, 2018 at 7 pm. According to our idea, it will be held at the main square of the city. For the ceremony we will prepare a special show with the famous speedcubers. In this regard, we recommend arriving in the city no later than 12.00 hours on June 7.\r\n\r\n2. The base fee allows to compete in 2x2x2 Cube, 3x3x3 Cube, Skewb, Pyraminx and Clock. For any other event you will need to pay additionally 1000 KZT per event.\r\n\r\n3. The winner of each event will receive a prize!\r\n\r\n===========\r\n\r\nБарлық қатысушылар мен қонақтардың назарына !!!\r\n1. Ресми ашылу 2018 жылдың 7 маусымында сағат 19.00-де өтеді, қаланың орталық алаңында өтеді. Салтанатты ашылу рәсімі үшін атақты спидкуберлер қатысуымен шоу-бағдарлама дайындалады. Осыған байланысты біз 7-маусымда сағат 12.00-ден кешіктірмей қалаға келуді ұсынамыз.\r\n\r\n2. Негізгі сыйақы 2x2x2 куб, 3x3x3 куб, Skewb, Pyraminx және Clock бойынша бәсекелесуге мүмкіндік береді. Кез-келген басқа іс-шараға қосымша бір оқиға үшін 1000 теңге төлеуге тура келеді.\r\n\r\n3. Әр жарыстың жеңімпазы жүлде алады.\r\n\r\n===========\r\n\r\nДополнительная информация:\r\n\r\nВнимание всем участникам и гостям!!!\r\n\r\n1. Официальная церемония открытия, состоится 7 июня 2018 года в 19.00 ч. По нашей задумке она будет проходить на главной площади города. Для церемонии будет подготовлена специальная шоу программа с участием именитых спидкуберов. В связи с этим рекомендуем прибыть в город не позднее 12.00 часов 7 июня.\r\n\r\n2. Регистрационный взнос позволяет принять участие в дисциплинах: 2х2, Rubik\'s Cube, Skweb, Piraminx, Clock. Для участия в других дисциплинах необходимо оплатить  дополнительный взнос по 1000 тенге за каждую дисциплину.  \r\n\r\n3. За первое место во всех дисциплинах предусмотрены призы', 2018, 6, 8, 2018, 6, 9, 0, '222 333 333bf 333fm 333ft 333mbf 333oh 444 444bf 555 555bf 666 777 clock minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Nikolay Masson (Николай Массон)}{mailto:nmasson@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Alikhan Yertursyn (Алихан Ертурсын)}{mailto:a.ertursyn@gmail.com}] [{Arman Mashimov (Арман Машимов)}{mailto:a_mashimov@mail.ru}] [{Hanneke Rijks}{mailto:hannekerijks@gmail.com}] [{Mats Valk}{mailto:matsvalk@gmail.com}] [{Roman Strakhov}{mailto:fpmk2@ya.ru}] [{Ron van Bruchem}{mailto:rbruchem@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[Nazarbayev Intellectual school of Physics and Mathematics](http://nis.edu.kz/en/schools/nis-semei/)', 'Karagaily St 1, Semey 071404, Kazakhstan', '', NULL, 'Semey Open 2018', 50454897, 80243879),
	('SerbianOpen2019', 'Serbian Open 2019', 'Belgrade', 'Serbia', 'Serbian Open 2019 je speedcubing takmičenje. Svako moze da se takmiči, nezavisno od njihove nacionalnosti ili godina, ali moraju biti upoznati sa WCA Regulacijama. Ovo takmičenje je priznato i kao Srpsko Nacionalno Prvenstvo.\r\n\r\n------------------------\r\n\r\nSerbian Open 2019 is a speedcubing competition. Anyone can participate, no matter which nationality or age they are, but they need to be familiar with the WCA Regulations. This competition is also recognized as a Serbian National Championship.', 2019, 3, 2, 2019, 3, 3, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 666 777 clock minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Dominik Vidaković}{mailto:dvidakovic@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Mihai Căpăţinescu}{mailto:mcapatinescu@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Aleksa Ilić}{mailto:ilic.alexa99@gmail.com}] [{Aleksa Radovanović}{mailto:aradovanovic@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Dominik Vidaković}{mailto:dvidakovic@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Mihai Căpăţinescu}{mailto:mcapatinescu@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[Mathematical Grammar School](https://www.mg.edu.rs)', 'Kraljice Natalije 37, Beograd 11000, Srbija', 'Pratite znakove da dođete do hale. / Follow the signs to the venue. ', NULL, 'Serbian Open 2019', 44809148, 20461400),
	('SharetSchool2018', 'Sharet School 2018', 'Netanya', 'Israel', 'Competition limited to 120 persons.\r\n\r\n* אם יש באפשרותכם להביא טיימרים רשמיים לתחרות, נודה לכם על העזרה\r\n* If you can provide an official timer, we will appreciate your help.', 2018, 3, 25, 2018, 3, 25, 0, '222 333', '[{Amit Sheffer}{mailto:asheffer@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Amit Sheffer}{mailto:asheffer@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Paola Levy}{mailto:paulatelem@gmail.com}]', 'School Gym', 'Sharet school, Zilber 14, Netanya', '', NULL, 'Sharet School 2018', 32342809, 34865815),
	('SmartCubersEgypt2019', 'Smart Cubers Egypt 2019', 'Hurghada', 'Egypt', 'Please read the \"More Info. / معلومات اخرى\" tab.', 2019, 6, 22, 2019, 6, 22, 0, '222 333 444', '[{Aysha Jamsheer}{mailto:ajamsheer@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Clément Cherblanc}{mailto:ccherblanc@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Mohamed Salem Diab}{mailto:mohamed_diaaab@yahoo.com}]', 'Long Beach Resort Hurghada', 'Sahl Hashish Rd, Hurghada', '', NULL, 'Smart Cubers Egypt 2019', 27081306, 33859250),
	('SpeedcubingPaphos2019', 'Speedcubing Paphos 2019', 'Paphos', 'Cyprus', ' Please read important information on \"Registration requirements\".\r\n', 2019, 9, 21, 2019, 9, 21, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 pyram skewb', '[{Mihai Căpăţinescu}{mailto:mcapatinescu@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Michael Eleftheriades}{mailto:eleftheriadesm@gmail.com}] [{Mihai Căpăţinescu}{mailto:mcapatinescu@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Shamil Magomedov}{mailto:smagomedov@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Theodosia Kyriakou}{mailto:kyriakoutheodosia30@gmail.com}]', '[The International School of Paphos](http://www.paphosinternationalschool.com/en/)', ' 100 Aristotelous Savva Avenue, Anavargos, Paphos, Cyprus', 'B BLOCK EXAMINATIONS HALL', 'http://cypruscubing.com', 'Speedcubing Paphos 2019', 34800227, 32450693),
	('SpeedcubingSlovakia2022', 'Speedcubing Slovakia 2022', 'Bratislava', 'Slovakia', '![](https://i.imgur.com/CDJ3dyD.png)\r\n\r\nPrvá súťaž na Slovensku od začiatku pandémie. Všetci sú vítaní :D\r\n\r\n---\r\nFirst competition in Slovakia since the pandemic started. Everyone is welcome :D', 2022, 8, 13, 2022, 8, 14, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 666 777 clock minx skewb', '[{Hubert Hanusiak}{mailto:hhanusiak@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Adam Brestovanský}{mailto:brestovanskyadam20@gmail.com}] [{Marek Majerik}{mailto:marecek.majerik@gmail.com}] [{Šimon Borovský}{mailto:sborovsky@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[Budova Vedeckého parku UK v Bratislave](https://cusp.uniba.sk/o-vedeckom-parku/)', 'Ilkovičova 8, 841 04 Karlova Ves, Slovakia', 'First floor', NULL, 'Speedcubing Slovakia 2022', 48149525, 17073370),
	('SundaySilenceSingapore2022', 'Sunday Silence Singapore 2022', 'Singapore', 'Singapore', 'While guests are permitted,  we recommend that any accompanying guests should wait in TripleOne Somerset Mall so as to not distract the competitors.  Guests who remain in the venue must remain silent when events are ongoing. Guests and/or competitors that are disruptive may be asked to leave the venue.', 2022, 7, 24, 2022, 7, 24, 0, '333fm 333mbf 444bf 555bf', '[{Zhou Yichen (周奕臣)}{mailto:yzhou@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Carmen Teo Bin Jie (张斌婕)}{mailto:carmmteo@gmail.com}] [{Wong Chong Wen (黄崇文)}{mailto:wongchongwench@gmail.com}]', 'Umazing Events @ TripleOne Somerset', '111 Somerset Road, Singapore 238164', '[#11-22 TripleOne Somerset]()', 'https://sites.google.com/view/sunday-silence-singapore', 'Sunday Silence Singapore 2022', 1300197, 103837349),
	('SwisscubingCupIV2023', 'Swisscubing Cup IV 2023', 'Vaduz (LI)', 'Liechtenstein', 'Swisscubing Cup IV ist Teil des Swisscubing Cup 2023. Dieser besteht aus 6 Competitions über das ganze Jahr verteilt. Um mehr darüber zu erfahren, besuche https://swisscubing.ch/swisscubing-cup-2023/.\r\nTeilnehmer die sich registrieren aber nicht bezahlen, müssen die Teilnahmegebühr bei ihrer nächsten Competition in der Schweiz bezahlen.\r\n______________________________________________________________________________________________\r\n\r\nSwisscubing Cup IV is part of the Swisscubing Cup 2023, made of 6 competitions during the whole year. Check out on https://swisscubing.ch/swisscubing-cup-2023/ for the details of the other editions.\r\nA competitor who registers and doesn\'t show up at the competition will have to pay that registration fee at his next competition in Switzerland.', 2023, 6, 24, 2023, 6, 25, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 444bf 555 minx pyram', '[{Ioannis Papadopoulos}{mailto:ipapadopoulos@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Mattia Pasquini}{mailto:mpasquini@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Stefan Loosli}{mailto:stee.loosli@gmail.com}] [{Swisscubing}{mailto:board@swisscubing.ch}]', '[Spörry Halle](https://www.vaduzer-saal.li/spoerry-areal/mehrzweckhalle)', 'Rüfestrasse 6, 9490 Vaduz, Liechtenstein', 'Mehrzweckhalle', NULL, 'Swisscubing Cup IV 2023', 47150173, 9516305),
	('TajikistanOpen2019', 'Tajikistan Open 2019', 'Khujand', 'Tajikistan', 'The competition is open to everyone.\r\n', 2019, 8, 24, 2019, 8, 25, 0, '222 333 333bf 333ft 333oh 444 555 clock minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Igor Aipkin}{mailto:iaipkin@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Igor Aipkin}{mailto:iaipkin@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Shukrullo Ibragimov}{mailto:tajikman12345@gmail.com}]', 'American Space in Khujand', 'Kalandarov str., 56', 'Grey 1 floor building near \"Nuri Islom\" mosque', NULL, 'Tajikistan Open 2019', 40302775, 69627581),
	('TbilisiSummerOpen2023', 'Tbilisi Summer Open 2023', 'Tbilisi', 'Georgia', '[GE]\r\nგთხოვთ, სახელი და გვარი შეავსოთ ზუსტად ისე როგორც მოცემულია თქვენს პირადობის დამადასტურებელ საბუთში. ინგლისურად შევსებისას, სახელის და გვარის პირველი ასო ჩაწერეთ დიდი ასოებით. პირადობის დამადასტურებელი საბუთი თან იქონიეთ შეჯიბრზე გამოცხადებისას.\r\nსტუმრის რაოდენობა შეზღუდულია (1 მონაწილეს შესაძლებელია თან ახლდეს მაქსიმუმ 1 გულშემატკივარი) - გულშემატკივრის დასწრება უფასოა\r\nვინც პირველად იღებთ მონაწილეობას აუცილებლად თან იქონიეთ პირადობის ან დაბადების მოწმობა \r\n\r\n[EN]\r\nPlease enter your name and surname during registration as it is writter on your ID.\r\nThe First letters are capital letters.\r\nDont forget to have an ID card with you when you come to the competition\r\nHere is Guest limitation (1 guest for each competitor) - its free to attend Guest\r\nFirst Timer competitors must have ID Card or birthday Certificate ', 2023, 6, 11, 2023, 6, 11, 0, '222 333 333oh minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Conan Mo}{mailto:conan@speedcubing.org.au}] [{Vako Marchilashvili (ვაკო მარჩილაშვილი)}{mailto:vmarchilashvili@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Vako Marchilashvili (ვაკო მარჩილაშვილი)}{mailto:vmarchilashvili@worldcubeassociation.org}]', 'Institute of Cybernetic (კიბერნეტიკის ინსტიტუტი)', 'Institute of Cybernetic (კიბერნეტიკის ინსტიტუტი)', '2 Floor , ( მეორე სართული  )', NULL, 'Tbilisi Summer Open 2023', 41723067, 44715356),
	('TeclaRubik2017', 'Tecla Rubik 2017', 'Santa Tecla', 'El Salvador', 'El costo de la inscripción es de $5.00 en Pre-Inscripcion y $6 el dia del evento. (Incluye participación en todas las categorías). \r\nEl Registro debera hacerse en esta pagina, se tomaran datos de competidor el dia del evento pero esto agregara $1 al costo de inscripcion. \r\n-Se podra pagar previamente en la cuenta detallada en la Pestaña de \"Informacion de Pago\" con un costo de $5. \r\n-El dia del evento la inscripcion tendra un costo de $6.', 2017, 5, 6, 2017, 5, 6, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 pyram', '[{Joel Hernández}{mailto:jhernandez@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Joel Hernández}{mailto:jhernandez@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Luis Salvador Batarsé Soto}{mailto:luisbatarse6@gmail.com}]', '[Palacio Tecleño](https://www.facebook.com/palaciosantatecla)', '2da avenida Nte y Paseo Concepción,  No. 2-1 Santa Tecla, El Salvador', 'Plaza Central', NULL, 'Tecla Rubik 2017', 13675693, -89289391),
	('TegucigalpaOpen2022', 'Tegucigalpa Open 2022', 'Tegucigalpa', 'Honduras', 'Tegucigalpa Open 2022 es el tan anhelado regreso de las competencias al pais, se contara con premios para los primeros lugares de cada categoria y sera un evento abierto a competidores de cualquier nacionalidad.\r\n\r\nTegucigalpa Open 2022 is the long-awaited return of competitions to the country, there will be prizes for the first places in each category and it will be an event open to competitors of any nationality.', 2022, 6, 26, 2022, 6, 26, 0, '222 333 333bf 444 pyram skewb sq1', '[{Luis David Hernández Mejía}{mailto:lmejia@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Erick Y. Maldonado}{mailto:erickyahirm@yahoo.com}] [{Gabriel Alejandro Obando Gonzalez}{mailto:gabrielobando2001@gmail.com}] [{Luis David Hernández Mejía}{mailto:lmejia@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Mauricio Daniel Salgado Carrillo}{mailto:maurydaniel10@yahoo.com}]', 'Universidad Autónoma de Honduras', 'Justo al costado de la Vicerrectoria Academica', 'Plaza Registro ', NULL, 'Tegucigalpa Open 2022', 14083897, -87163190),
	('TheMostSerene2016', 'The Most Serene Competition 2016', 'Dogana', 'San Marino', 'Competitors limit is 40.\r\nRegistration fee is 5€, free for citizens of San Marino.', 2016, 8, 27, 2016, 8, 27, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555', '[{Lorenzo Vigani Poli}{mailto:lpoli@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Matteo Colombo}{mailto:matte.colo@gmail.com}]', '[{Filippo Brancaleoni}{mailto:f.brancaleoni@protonmail.com}] [{Tommaso Zoffoli}{mailto:tommasozoffoli@gmail.com}]', '[Centro Atlante San Marino](http://www.centroatlante.com/)', 'Via Tre Settembre, 17, 47891 Dogana, San Marino', '', 'http://cubingitaly.org/rsm2016', 'The Most Serene Competition 2016', 43977274, 12486523),
	('ThePeponiHouseTwistTurn2023', 'The Peponi House Twist & Turn 2023', 'Nairobi', 'Kenya', 'Welcome to the third WCA competition in Kenya! \r\nThis competition is specifically created for those who are aged 13 and under. Those who are aged 14 and above can participate... but will not qualify to get a prize on the podium.\r\n\r\nParticipants should bring some form of identification in order to confirm that they are aged 13 and below. A passport, or a copy of your birth cirtificate is a good example since it shows name, age, nationality and so on.  \r\n\r\nYou only need to be present at the venue during the events in which you plan to attend. However, you need to be present at the venue no later than 15 minutes before your first event starts so that you have enough time to complete the registration.', 2023, 5, 13, 2023, 5, 13, 0, '222 333 pyram', '[{Rayan Parmar}{mailto:rparmar@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Nikhath Zigmund}{mailto:nikhathakhtar@gmail.com}]', 'Peponi House Preparatory School', 'Peponi House Preparatory School, Farasi Lane, Nairobi, Kenya', 'Main Hall', NULL, 'Peponi House Twist & Turn 2023', -1241111, 36760382),
	('TunisiaWinterOpenDay2017', 'Tunisia Winter Open Day 2017', 'Sousse', 'Tunisia', 'Tunisia Winter Open 2017 is open for participants from all countries, everyone is welcome.\r\nCompetition fee is 20DT per participant\r\nMedals and Gifts will be awarded to the winners in each category.\r\nIt should be known that only competitors who do check-in into the hotel can benefit from the lunch.', 2017, 12, 20, 2017, 12, 20, 0, '222 333 333bf 333mbf 333oh 444 444bf 555 555bf 666 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Mohamed Ali Bizid}{mailto:mbizid@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Raouf Thabet}{mailto:raoufh.thabet@laposte.net}]', 'Hotel Marhaba Palace Sousse', 'BP N120، Hammam Sousse 4089, Tunisie', 'Look for the conference room inside the hotel', NULL, 'Tunisia Winter Open Day 2017', 35896540, 10593775),
	('TurnininTermonfeckinSun2023', 'Turnin\' in Termonfeckin Sunday 2023', 'Termonfeckin, Drogheda, Louth', 'Ireland', '![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBczBoIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--96b6278788e78960bf29ec7536273758105149bb/Bordered%20Logo.png)\r\n\r\nhttps://speedcubingireland.com/\r\nAdd us on [Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/speedcubingireland/) and [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/speedcubingireland/?hl=en)! Join our [Discord Server](https://discord.gg/ddFb3WeTx8)!\r\n\r\n', 2023, 3, 12, 2023, 3, 12, 0, '222 333 333bf 555 clock minx pyram sq1', '[{Maria Beausang}{mailto:mbeausang@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Simon Kelly}{mailto:skelly@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Maria Beausang}{mailto:mbeausang@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Speedcubing Ireland}{mailto:speedcubingireland@gmail.com}]', 'St Fechins GAA Club', 'Pairc Naomh Feichín, Termonfeckin, Drogheda, Co. Louth', '', NULL, 'Turnin\' in Termonfeckin Sun 2023', 53736092, -6301848),
	('UCOMParaguay2023', 'UCOM Paraguay 2023', 'Asunción', 'Paraguay', '**¡Formá parte de este nuevo torneo!**\r\nRecordá que para participar es obligatorio estar familiarizado con el [Reglamento de la WCA](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/translations/spanish-american/)\r\n\r\n¡Te necesitamos para seguir fortaleciendo nuestra comunidad! Involucrate con las diferentes tareas que nos ayudan a un torneo exitoso y agradable para todos, ya sea como juez, runner, scrambler, etc. Te dejamos links para más información a continuación:\r\n\r\n *[Reglas basicas sobre cómo competir](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8O_iWRGq4K8)\r\n *[Manual WCA para competidores](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/edudoc/competitor-tutorial/es/tutorial.pdf)\r\n *[Manual WCA para jueces](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/edudoc/judge-tutorial/judge-tutorial-es.pdf)\r\n\r\nTe esperamos :)\r\n\r\n**Be part of this new tournament!**\r\nRemember that to participate it is mandatory to be familiar with the [\"WCA Regulations\"](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/)\r\n\r\nWe need you to continue strengthening our community! Get involved with the different tasks that help us to have a successful and enjoyable tournament for everyone, be it as a judge, runner, scrambler, etc. We leave you links for more information below:\r\n\r\n *[Basics rules to compete](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dPL3eV-A0ww)\r\n *[WCA competitor tutorial](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/edudoc/competitor-tutorial/tutorial.pdf)\r\n *[WCA judging tutorial](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/edudoc/judge-tutorial/judge-tutorial.pdf)\r\n\r\nSee you there :)\r\n\r\nCLUB DE SPEEDCUBING PARAGUAY\r\nEmail: speedcubingpy@gmail.com\r\nFacebook: [/cscpy](https://web.facebook.com/cscpy/)\r\nInstagram: [@cscpy](https://www.instagram.com/cscpy/)', 2023, 4, 15, 2023, 4, 16, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 666 777 clock minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Elias Miguel Acosta Acosta}{mailto:eacosta@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Gustavo Riveiro}{mailto:griveiro@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Griselda Mendieta}{mailto:grisel94@gmail.com}] [{Gustavo Riveiro}{mailto:griveiro@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Hermes López}{mailto:samulopez424@gmail.com}]', '[Universidad Comunera] (https://ucom.edu.py)', 'Monseñor Bogarín 284 esq. Dr. Juan Eulogio Estigarribia', 'Salón Auditorio', NULL, 'UCOM Paraguay 2023', -25294426, -57583583),
	('UNACHIOpen2022', 'UNACHI Open 2022', 'David, Chiriquí', 'Panama', '**Español**\r\n•	“UNACHI Open 2022” será la quinta competencia oficial en Chiriquí.\r\n•	Buscamos seguir impulsando el speedcubing en Panamá, dando la bienvenida a nuevos competidores.\r\n•	El uso de la mascarilla es obligatorio en todo momento dentro de la competencia.\r\n•	Los resultados preliminares, y los clasificados a rondas posteriores, se podrán ver casi en tiempo real en WCA Live.\r\n\r\n**English**\r\n• \"UNACHI Open 2022\" will be the fifth official competition in Chiriquí.\r\n• We seek to continue promoting speedcubing in Panama, welcoming new competitors.\r\n• The use of the mask is mandatory at all times inside the venue.\r\n• Preliminary results, and those qualified for subsequent rounds, can be viewed in near real-time on WCA Live.\r\n![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbDhoIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--4810b4c2ee0b16d132e23257cdbd01f3e4201b9c/UNACHI%20OPEN.png)', 2022, 10, 14, 2022, 10, 14, 0, '222 333 pyram skewb', '[{Egdar Castillo}{mailto:ecastillo@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Egdar Castillo}{mailto:ecastillo@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Egdar Rolando Castillo}{mailto:speedcubech@gmail.com}]', 'Universidad Autónoma de Chiriquí', 'Calle de la Unachi, David, Panamá', 'Cafetería de Ciencias', NULL, 'UNACHI Open 2022', 8433292, -82451545),
	('UsakOpen2022', 'Uşak Open 2022', 'Uşak', 'Turkey', '[TR]\r\nKayıt sırasında adınızı ve soyadınızı lütfen kimlikte yazıldığı gibi hatasız giriniz. İlk harfleri büyük yazınız.\r\nYarışmaya gelirken yanınızda kimlik bulundurmayı unutmayınız. **Lütfen sekmeleri okuyunuz.** \r\n\r\n[EN]\r\nPlease enter your name and surname during registration as it is written on your ID.\r\nThe First letters are capital letters.\r\nDont forget to have an ID card with you when you come to the competition. **Please read all the tabs.**', 2022, 4, 23, 2022, 4, 24, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 pyram skewb', '[{Can Ersoy}{mailto:cersoy@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{İskender Aznavur}{mailto:i.kuleli@gmail.com}] [{Melih Kayra Kadıoğlu}{mailto:melih0kayra@gmail.com}]', 'İskender Pala Halk Kütüphanesi Kurtuluş Mahallesi Doğan Özkahraman Caddesi No:20 Merkez, Uşak', 'Kurtuluş Mahallesi, Doğan Özkahraman Caddesi, No:20 Uşak, Merkez', 'İskender Pala Halk Kütüphanesi', NULL, 'Uşak Open 2022', 38673788, 29401551),
	('UTNIbarraOpen2023', 'UTN Ibarra Open 2023', 'Ibarra', 'Ecuador', 'Información detallada en las demás pestañas.\r\n\r\nPlease check the tabs for detailed information.', 2023, 7, 15, 2023, 7, 15, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 minx pyram skewb', '[{Jorge Contento}{mailto:jcontento@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Luis Fernando Aldás Cuestas}{mailto:ferchoaldas@hotmail.com}]', 'Universidad Técnica del Norte.', 'Av. 17 de Julio 5-21 y Gral. José María Córdova - Sector El Olivo', 'Polideportivo de Universidad.', NULL, 'UTN Ibarra Open 2023', 358563, -78112524),
	('UzbekistanOpen2018', 'Uzbekistan Open 2018', 'Tashkent', 'Uzbekistan', 'The competition is open to all but only citizens of Uzbekistan can win prizes.\r\n\r\nУчаствовать в соревновании могут все, но только граждане Узбекистана могут выиграть призы.\r\n\r\nMusobaqada har qanday ishtirokchi qatnasha oladi, sovg\'alar faqat O\'zbekiston fuqarolari uchun beriladi.', 2018, 8, 18, 2018, 8, 19, 0, '222 333 333bf 333mbf 333oh 444 555 666 777 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Akash Rupela}{mailto:arupela@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Akash Rupela}{mailto:arupela@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Clément Cherblanc}{mailto:ccherblanc@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Igor Aipkin}{mailto:iaipkin@worldcubeassociation.org}]', 'Atlas', 'Atlas, Tashkent city, Chilanzar district, Katartal str., 28', '4th Floor', NULL, 'Uzbekistan Open 2018', 41281733, 69201847),
	('ValceaRubikOpen2013', 'Valcea Rubik Open 2013', 'Ramnicu Valcea', 'Romania', 'Prima competitie de cub Rubik din Ramnicu Valcea. Va fi o competitie de o singura zi si speram la cat mai multi participanti pentru a repeta si in alti ani acest eveniment.', 2013, 11, 9, 2013, 11, 9, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444', '[{Radu Făciu}{mailto:radufaciu@gmail.com}]', '[{Mădălin Constantin Stoenete}{mailto:wrt+2012stoe01@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Sorin Veștemean}{mailto:newmagicfilms@gmail.com}]', '[River Plaza Mall](http://www.riverplaza.ro/)', 'Calea lui Traian nr. 125', 'Etajul 1', 'http://www.speedcubing.ro/p-55/valcea-rubik-open', 'Valcea Open 2013', 45099911, 24361817),
	('ValmieraOpen2022', 'Valmiera Open 2022', 'Valmiera', 'Latvia', 'Pirmās ātrkubošanas sacensības Valmierā. Nāc un sacenties ar citiem, un labi pavadīts laiks garantēts!\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nFirst speedcubing competition to be held in the city of Valmiera. Come and compete with others and have a great time!', 2022, 7, 30, 2022, 7, 30, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 555 clock pyram', '[{Jānis Zirnis}{mailto:jzirnis@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Vladislavs Baranovs}{mailto:vladislavs.baranovs@gmail.com}]', '[{Marks Cimermanis}{mailto:marks.cimermanis@gmail.com}]', '[Vidzemes augstskola inženierzinātņu fakultāte, T106](https://va.lv/lv) ', 'Valmiera Tērbatas iela 10', 'Go to the main entrance and follow the signs. Main entrance is from the garden side', NULL, 'Valmiera Open 2022', 57541644, 25428157),
	('VenezuelaOpen2013', 'Venezuela Open 2013', 'Mérida', 'Venezuela', 'Primer Torneo Oficial Venezolano.  [Página de Registro al Venezuela Open 2013](http://www.cubingsouthamerica.com/VenezuelaOpen/register.php)', 2013, 9, 29, 2013, 9, 29, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 555 minx pyram', '[{Wilson José Duarte Espitia}{mailto:wilsonjose.duarte@gmail.com}]', '[{Oscar Alberto Ceballos Contreras}{mailto:oscaralbertoceballos@gmail.com}]', '[Hotel Caribay](http://www.hotelcaribay.com)', 'Av. 2 Lora con Viaducto Miranda, Mérida Venezuela', 'Salón Zuhe', 'http://www.cubingsouthamerica.com/VenezuelaOpen', 'Venezuela Open 2013', 8589428, -71156306),
	('VeranoCubero2015', 'Verano Cubero 2015', 'Santo Domingo', 'Dominican Republic', 'Novena competencia oficial en Republica Dominicana', 2015, 8, 15, 2015, 8, 16, 0, '222 333 333bf 333fm 333ft 333oh 444 555 666 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Nestor Sanchez}{mailto:nestorsanchez3d@gmail.com}]', '[{Rafael Gregorio Martinez Paredes}{mailto:rparedes@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Sumi Lee}{mailto:misumilee@gmail.com}]', '[Galeria 360](http://www.galeria360.com.do)', 'Av. Jhon F. Kennedy casi esquina Av. Abraham Lincoln', 'Area de entrada, puerta principal.', 'http://www.cubingsouthamerica.com/veranocubero2015/', 'Verano Cubero 2015', 18484951, -69936111),
	('VeronaOpen2017', 'Verona Open 2017', 'Verona', 'Italy', 'There is a limit of 60 competitors.\r\n\r\nAt a certain point we\'ll send an email to confirm your participation; competitors who don\'t confirm within the date specified in that email will be deleted. \r\nRemember to check your inbox 1-2 weeks before the competiton.\r\n\r\n[![Image description](http://i.imgur.com/yztC4Jt.png) Clicka qui per il sito web in italiano](https://cubingitaly.org/verona-17)', 2017, 9, 24, 2017, 9, 24, 0, '222 333 333bf 333oh 444 pyram sq1', '[{Lorenzo Vigani Poli}{mailto:lpoli@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Matteo Provasi}{mailto:mprovasi@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Simone Cantarelli}{mailto:scantarelli@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Cubing Italy}{mailto:board@cubingitaly.org}] [{Giovanni Bezzetto}{mailto:giovanni.bezzetto@gmail.com}]', '[Corte Molon](http://www.cortemolonverona.it)', 'Via della Diga 17, 37124 Verona', '', 'https://cubingitaly.org/verona-17', 'Verona Open 2017', 45461250, 10956092),
	('VIDCubing2023', 'VID Cubing 2023', 'Hatillo 3, San Jose', 'Costa Rica', '**VID Cubing 2023** \r\n\r\nEs la segunda competencia del nuevo año 2023.\r\n\r\nEsta competencia es reconocida como una competencia official de la World Cube Association.\r\nLa competencia es abierta a competidores de cualquier nacionalidad, el registro esta habilitado desde la página oficial de la WCA. No es necesario tener experiencia, pero los competidores deben estar conocer los Reglamentos\r\nEl acceso a invitados y espectadores será gratuita.\r\n_____\r\n**English version**\r\n\r\n**VID Cubing 2023**\r\n\r\nIs a second competition of the new year 2023. \r\n\r\nThis competition is recognized as an official World Cube Association competition.\r\nThe competition is open to all competitors of all nationalities. Registration is available on the WCA website. No experience in WCA competitions is necessary, but competitors should be familiar with the WCA Regulations\r\nThe competition is free to spectators and guests.\r\n\r\n', 2023, 4, 29, 2023, 4, 29, 0, '222 333 333oh 444 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Marvin Solano}{mailto:msolano@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Norman López Delgado}{mailto:norman.lopez.delgado@gmail.com}]', '[VID](https://www.instagram.com/vid_ibecr/)', 'Hatillo 3, contiguo al Liceo Edgar Cervantes', 'Salón Principal', NULL, 'VID Cubing 2023', 9917322, -84100223),
	('VietnamChampionship2023', 'Vietnam Championship 2023', 'Ho Chi Minh City', 'Vietnam', 'Giải đấu Vô địch Việt Nam với tất cả các bộ môn, được tổ chức trong ba ngày. Các bạn có thể truy cập vào tab \"Schedule\" để xem thêm thông tin. \r\n\r\n---\r\nThe Vietnam Championship 2023 is a multi-event competition spanning 3 days. Please check \"Schedule\" tab for more information.\r\n\r\n**Please note**\r\nCompetitors of all nationalities are welcome,\r\n\r\nThere will be **2 types of winner** in this competition:\r\n**Open Category** - Top 3 winners of the competition regardless of nationality \r\n**Vietnamese Category** - Top 3 Vietnamese winners of the competition\r\n', 2023, 7, 14, 2023, 7, 16, 0, '222 333 333bf 333fm 333mbf 333oh 444 444bf 555 555bf 666 777 clock minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Ivan Lew Yi Wen (刘义文)}{mailto:iwen@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Lê Trần Đăng Quỳnh}{mailto:dangquynh1220@gmail.com}] [{Leow Yi Jun (廖艺畯)}{mailto:yleow@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Wang Junwen (王俊文)}{mailto:jwang@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Hiệp hội Rubik Việt Nam}{mailto:vncubeassociation@gmail.com}] [{Toan Do Cong}{mailto:tdo@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Zyorubik}{mailto:zyorubik@gmail.com}]', 'Nhà Thiếu Nhi Thành Phố Hồ Chí Minh (City Children\'s House)', '169 Đường Nam Kỳ Khởi Nghĩa, Phường 6, Quận 3, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh 700000', 'Hội trường Nhà Thiếu Nhi Thành Phố (The stage of the City Children\'s House)', NULL, 'Vietnam Championship 2023', 10783664, 106688640),
	('VillaCarlosPazOtono2019', 'Villa Carlos Paz Otoño 2019', 'Villa Carlos Paz, Córdoba', 'Argentina', 'VCP Otoño 2019 will be the second competition ever to be hosted in the province of Córdoba, Argentina. It will last two days and it will feature thirteen WCA events.\r\n\r\nVCP Otoño 2019 será la segunda competencia realizada en la Provincia de Córdoba, Argentina. Constará de dos días y se podrá competir en trece categorías distintas.', 2019, 4, 19, 2019, 4, 20, 0, '222 333 333bf 333mbf 333oh 444 555 666 777 minx pyram skewb sq1', '[{Cristian Ezequiel Vega}{mailto:cvega@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Agustín Bernasconi}{mailto:hammerwtf10@gmail.com}] [{Genaro Sahib Leguizamon}{mailto:genasahib01@gmail.com}]', 'Iglesia Vida Con Proposito', 'Gabriela Mistral 549, Chincheta, Villa Carlos Paz, Córdoba', '', NULL, 'Villa Carlos Paz Otoño 2019', -31413974, -64477627),
	('VillavicencioOpenII2018', 'Villavicencio Open II 2018', 'Villavicencio', 'Colombia', 'Limite de 50 competidores.\r\nCosto: $20.000 COP todos los eventos.\r\n\r\nCompetitor limit: 50.\r\nCost: $20.000COP (7USD aprox) for all events.', 2018, 8, 18, 2018, 8, 19, 0, '222 333 333bf 333fm 333oh minx pyram', '[{José Leonardo Chaparro Prieto}{mailto:jprieto@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{José Leonardo Chaparro Prieto}{mailto:jprieto@worldcubeassociation.org}]', 'Polideportivo García Bohórquez', 'Calle 19 #37I-54', '', NULL, 'Villavicencio Open II 2018', 4135106, -73635030),
	('VilniusWinterOpen2023', 'Vilnius Winter Open 2023', 'Vilnius', 'Lithuania', 'Dalyviai, dalyvaujantis tik vienoje rungtyje varžybose dalyvauja nemokamai.\r\nReguliariai tikrinkite savo elektroninio pašto dėžutę dėl patvirtinimo laiško ir naujos informacijos dėl varžybų.\r\n\r\nCompetitors competing in only one event participate for free.\r\nRegularly check your email inbox for confirmation email and updates about the competition.\r\n\r\n', 2023, 1, 14, 2023, 1, 15, 0, '222 333 333bf 333mbf 333oh 444 555 666 777 clock pyram skewb sq1', '[{Kasparas Lienys}{mailto:klienys@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Eimantas Vansevičius}{mailto:eimantas.vansevicius@gmail.com}] [{Kasparas Lienys}{mailto:klienys@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Žygimantas Ežerskis}{mailto:ezygis2008@gmail.com}]', '[Žemynos progimnazija](https://zemynosprogimnazija.lt/)', 'Žemynos gatvė 14, Vilnius, Vilniaus miesto savivaldybė', 'On the first floor, follow the signs', NULL, 'Vilnius Winter Open 2023', 54728480, 25232419),
	('VinderupOpen2016', 'Vinderup Open 2016', 'Vinderup', 'Denmark', 'Registration fee is 50dkr, it is possible to sleep at the venue (contact organiser)', 2016, 10, 8, 2016, 10, 9, 0, '222 333 333bf 333mbf 333oh 444 444bf 555 555bf 666 777 minx pyram skewb', '[{Henrik Buus Aagaard}{mailto:haagaard@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Karina Grandjean Beck}{mailto:karinagrandjeanbeck@gmail.com}]', '[Vinderup Realskole](http://www.vinderup-real.dk/)', 'Vinderup Realskole, Sevelvej 42, 7830 Vinderup', '', NULL, 'Vinderup Open 2016', 56478631, 8784360),
	('VoruVark2019', 'Võru Värk 2019', 'Võru', 'Estonia', '* The main event of this competition is **2x2x2 Cube**.\r\n* This is the first competition in **Võru**.\r\n![Eesti kuubik](https://i.imgur.com/Cr7XSizt.png)\r\n\r\n', 2019, 4, 6, 2019, 4, 6, 0, '222 333 333oh clock pyram skewb', '[{Andreas Pung}{mailto:apung@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Ivo Kruusamägi}{mailto:ikruusamagi@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Remo Pihel}{mailto:remopihel@gmail.com}] [{Rio Truija}{mailto:riotruija1@gmail.com}]', '[Võru City Center School](http://www.vkk.edu.ee/en/)', 'Vabaduse 12, Võru, 65609 Võru maakond, Estonia', 'On the fourth floor, follow the signs.', NULL, 'Võru Värk 2019', 57845490, 26996713),
	('VossOpen2019', 'Voss Open 2019', 'Voss', 'Norway', 'Everyone who can solve a cube are welcome to participate in this competition!\r\n\r\n-----\r\n\r\nAlle som kan løse kube er velkomne til å delta i denne konkurransen!', 2019, 2, 23, 2019, 2, 24, 0, '222 333 333ft 333oh 444 555 minx pyram skewb', '[{Ulrik Bredland}{mailto:ubredland@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[{Ivar Strangstadstuen}{mailto:tre141592653589793238462643383@gmail.com}] [{Jonatan Solheim}{mailto:tilingen@gmail.com}]', 'Voss Folkehøgskule', 'Eskelandsvegen 28, 5704 Voss', 'Olavsalen', 'http://kubing.no/events/vo2019/', 'Voss Open 2019', 60625530, 6390886),
	('VoulaSummerOpen2023', 'Voula Summer Open 2023', 'Voula - Athens', 'Greece', '![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbUUvIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--25a11a161841639a3cff2ecfb046c27deb82697e/Cubestore_VSO23_post.jpg)\r\n\r\nΤο Voula Summer Open 2023 είναι ο 3oς WCA διαγωνισμός στην Ελλάδα για το 2023. Είμαστε περήφανοι για την πορεία μας φέτος και συνεχίζουμε δυναμικά. Στη σειρά διαγωνισμών \"Road to Greek Nationals\" εστιάζουμε σε κάθε διαγωνισμό σε 2 events που δεν είναι ακόμα πολύ γνωστά στην Ελλάδα. Σε αυτό το διαγωνισμό θέλουμε να φέρουμε στο ελληνικό κοινό τα αγωνίσματα του One Handed/Λύση με ένα χέρι και του Fewest Move Challenge (FMC)/Δοκιμασία λύσης με τις λιγότερες κινήσεις πιο κοντά στους συμμετέχοντες. Ο στόχος μας είναι να διεξαχθεί το πρώτο εθνικό πρωτάθλημα της Ελλάδας προς το τέλος του τρέχοντος έτους. Μέχρι τότε, όλα τα WCA events θα είναι οικεία στους συμμετέχοντες. Πάρτε τους κύβους σας, ετοιμαστείτε, διαβάστε τους κανόνες και ελάτε στην γιορτή του cubing!\r\n\r\nΠαρακαλoύμε διαβάστε αναλυτικά τις επόμενες σελίδες για να βρείτε όλες τις απαραίτητες πληροφορίες. \r\n\r\nΣημείωση: Για να θεωρείται ολοκληρωμένη μία εγγραφή πρέπει να ολοκληρωθεί το registration στο σελίδα του διαγωνισμού στην WCA **KAI** να γίνει και η πληρωμή του αντιτίμου συμμετοχής με χρήση της τραπεζικής σας κάρτας μέσω της πλατφόρμας πληρωμών stripe που χρησιμοποιεί η WCA, όπως περιγράφεται στις καρτέλες δίπλα. \r\n\r\n[Εγγραφή στη WCA, σε επίσημο διαγωνισμό και πολλά ακόμα. Οδηγός για πρωτάρηδες.](https://youtu.be/RS768gK0Vrg)\r\n\r\nThe Voula Open 2023 is the third competition this year in Greece. We are proud of our progress and we strongly continue our effort. Grab your cubes, get ready, read the rules, and come to the cubing celebration!\r\nDuring  each \"Road to Greek finals\" competition, we focus on 2 events that are not yet very well known in Greece. In this competition we are aiming to bring the events One Handed and Fewest Move Challenge (FMC) closer to the competitors. The goal is to make the first Greek National Championship towards the end of this year. By then, all WCA events will be familiar to the competitors.\r\n\r\nGrab your cubes, study the regulations and attend the greek feast of cubing!\r\n\r\nPlease read the following tabs very carefully!\r\n\r\nNote: For a registration to be considered valid, the competitor should both register though the WCA site **AND** pay the registration fee as described in the nexts tabs.\r\nPlease read the following tabs in detail to find all the necessary information.', 2023, 7, 15, 2023, 7, 16, 0, '222 333 333fm 333oh 444 clock minx pyram skewb', '[{Ioannis Papadopoulos}{mailto:ipapadopoulos@worldcubeassociation.org}] [{Kostas Papadopoulos}{mailto:kwpaptypetomaniac97@gmail.com}] [{Michael Eleftheriades}{mailto:eleftheriadesm@gmail.com}]', '[{Christos Dimizas}{mailto:cdimizas@otenet.gr}]', '\"Ιωνία\" Πολιτιστικό Κέντρο / \"Ionia\" Caltural Center', 'Λεωφ. Κωνσταντίνου Καραμανλή 113, Βούλα 166 73', 'Culture Centre', NULL, 'Voula Summer Open 2023', 37836297, 23766522),
	('WAMozart2010', 'Abierto W. A. Mozart 2010', 'Santiago', 'Chile', 'La cuota de inscripción es de $1.500. Fecha límite de registo es el 20 de Nov a las 23:59hrs.\r\nSe celebrarán eventos no-oficiales: 2x2 one-handed, 2x2 blindfolded y Floppy Cube.', 2010, 12, 11, 2010, 12, 11, 0, '222 333 magic mmagic pyram', '[{Sebastián Pino Castillo}{mailto:sebastian.pino.c@gmail.com}]', '[{Jaime Pinto}{mailto:wrt+2009pint01@worldcubeassociation.org}]', '[Colegio W. A. Mozart](http://www.colegiomozart.cl/)', 'Javiera Carrera Sur #564, La Reina', 'Casino 2º Piso', 'http://www.armaelcubo.com/inicio/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=44%3Amozart2010&catid=35%3Amozart2010&Itemid=1', 'WA Mozart 2010', -33458591, -70566717),
